// Timer Timer:  0:00 Pause Go Game Over Pause Resume Phase One Instructions 
\Instructions:
\ - The Scroggle board is made up of 9 mini boards.\ - Within each mini board, create words of 3+ letters.\ - Letters must be selected in spelling order.\ - Click the corresponding B button to submit the word.\ - Unselect the letters in the order they were selected.\ - Points are awarded by letter similar to Scrabble.\ - 9-letter words formed in phase 1 are worth double points.\ - Each invalid word that is submitted has a penalty of -3 points (0 is the min score).\ - The game is 3 minutes long. The first 1.5 minutes is phase 1. The second half of the time is phase 2.\ - Once time runs out, the game is over.
\
