// Phase two Phase Two Instructions 
\Instructions:
\ - Phase One is over, you are now entering Phase Two.\ - You will have 10 seconds to select one letter from each mini board.\ - Choose your letters wisely as points are now doubled for all letters and a 9 letter word is worth triple!\ - Likewise, an invalid word will be penalized.\ - You have 1.5min to create a new word from these letters.\ - Hit the !! button to submit your word.\
